{"tid":767947,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電台化驗恩平溫泉酒店水辦 含菌量超國家標準1至5倍","createTime":"2018-08-05T03:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T04:51:59.000Z","uid":70063,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4288331a20f2f5a3f0e3eb8e30000976748485b","tid":767947,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波之前談及大灣區規劃時，曾建議市民可以到廣東恩平浸溫泉。本台記者上月中，到恩平5間溫泉酒店，抽取20多個水辦，交予浸會大學化驗。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現全部樣本的含菌量，超出國家衛生標準1至5倍，如果按照香港泳池的衛生標準，含菌量更超標10至50倍。<br />\n<br />\n在部分水辦內溫泉水應有的化學物質含量，亦未達到國家標準最低要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2089227527851959/UzpfSTM1OTgyNTc1NzQwNTMxNDoxNzYxMTM0NDkzOTQxMDkz/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2089227527851959%2FUzpfSTM1OTgyNTc1NzQwNTMxNDoxNzYxMTM0NDkzOTQxMDkz%2F&d=OF85xTxwdB8Jrd18ODRdZ%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=18b4987a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2089227527851959/UzpfSTM1OTgyNTc1NzQwNTMxNDoxNzYxMTM0NDkzOTQxMDkz/</a>"},{"pid":"df37c10a4712172b3e387d08323d6dfd44f3cff4","tid":767947,"uid":4816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab6089d3a95feb6728ce7f4cae696f21ba659ac","tid":767947,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c7f01a52c8d10538a9a99e9e6e0a02b6959bb6","tid":767947,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"香港電台為香港特別行政區政府商務及經濟發展局轄下的部門，而商務及經濟發展局是由財政司司長領導的決策局<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"h